            "mBlockImage": "shopify://shop_images/Summer_Lawn-m.png",
            "tag": "Free with 1st order",
            "heading": "Summer Lawn",
            "details": "Crafted by our scent experts to capture the unmistakable scent of freshly cut grass with citrus, bergamot and mint.",
            "expend-label": "blend details",
            "expendable-content": "<div>\n    <h4 class=\"font-lausanne\">Top notes</h4>\n    <ul>\n      <li class=\"font-lausanne fw-200\">\n            <span class=\"fw-400\">Bergamot</span>\n            <br> Sweet and citrusy\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"font-lausanne fw-200\">\n            <span class=\"fw-400\">Leaf alcohol </span>\n            <br> Green and herbaceous\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"font-lausanne fw-200\">\n            <span class=\"fw-400\">Galbanum </span>\n            <br> Leafy and fresh\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"font-lausanne fw-200\">\n            <span class=\"fw-400\">Eau de Cologne min </span>\n            <br> Citrusy and minty\n        </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h4 class=\"font-lausanne\">Middle Notes</h4>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"font-lausanne fw-200\">\n            <span class=\"fw-400\">Linden blossom </span>\n            <br>Fresh and floral\n        </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h4 class=\"font-lausanne\">Base Notes</h4>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"font-lausanne fw-200\">\n            <span class=\"fw-400\">Copaiba balsam  </span>\n            <br>Gentle and woody\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"font-lausanne fw-200\">\n            <span class=\"fw-400\">Coumarin  </span>\n            <br>Warm and sweet\n        </li>\n    </ul>\n</div>"
          }
        },
        "image_prBBn8": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
